OL,3,C'Coronation Street storyline made me
OL,4,Cseek help from abusive partner'
OL,6,FRachel Bullock investigates the scale
OL,7,Fof violence against women in the North
OL,8,FEast for this special report
OL,10,FA victim of domestic abuse says she
OL,11,Fwas inspired to seek help after
OL,12,Fwatching a storyline on the subject on
OL,13,FCoronation Street.
OL,15,FBecky, not her real name, has been
OL,16,Fsharing her experience of abuse as she
OL,17,Furged other victims to recognise their
OL,18,F"worth" and access support.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/15
