OL,3,C'Coronation Street storyline made me
OL,4,Cseek help from abusive partner'
OL,6,FBut it was thanks to a storyline on
OL,7,Fthe cobbles of ITV's long-running soap
OL,8,Fopera that prompted Becky to act.
OL,10,F"It was a massive eye-opener because I
OL,11,Fcould identify the behaviours," she
OL,12,Fcontinued. "I think some women don't
OL,13,Fwant to admit that their relationship
OL,14,Fisn't what they post on Instagram or
OL,15,FFacebook.
OL,17,F"But you're a lot stronger than you
OL,18,Fthink, and there are so many
OL,19,Forganisations who can help you. Your
OL,20,Flife is worth a lot more than he makes
OL,21,Fyou feel it is."
