OL,3,C'Coronation Street storyline made me
OL,4,Cseek help from abusive partner'
OL,6,FBecky's story comes as the most recent
OL,7,Fdata from the Office Of National
OL,8,FStatistics shows the North East has
OL,9,Fsome of the highest rates of violence
OL,10,Fagainst the person, classed as
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse-related offences.
OL,13,FLast year, Cleveland Police recorded
OL,14,F24.5 cases of domestic abuse per 1,000
OL,15,Fpeople - placing the force with the
OL,16,Fsecond highest rate in England and
OL,17,FWales.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/15
