OL,3,C'Coronation Street storyline made me
OL,4,Cseek help from abusive partner'
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Northumbria Police recorded
OL,7,F18 per 1,000, Durham Police recorded
OL,8,F19.6 per 1,000 and North Yorkshire
OL,9,FPolice handled 10.3.
OL,11,FDespite these stark figures, Becky
OL,12,Fbelieves they only scratch the surface.
OL,14,F"I think it's a lot more common than
OL,15,Fthe stats show because a lot of women
OL,16,Fstill have that fear of coming
OL,17,Fforward," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/15
