OL,3,C'Coronation Street storyline made me
OL,4,Cseek help from abusive partner'
OL,6,FAnd WWIN, the specialist domestic
OL,7,Fabuse service which supported her,
OL,8,Ftold ITV Tyne Tees that referrals this
OL,9,Fyear are at a record high.
OL,11,FThe new Labour government describes
OL,12,Fthe scale of the problem as a national
OL,13,Femergency and for the first time has
OL,14,Fappointed a minister specifically to
OL,15,Ftackle violence against women and
OL,16,Fgirls.
OL,18,FJess Phillips is that minister and, in
OL,19,Fthe past, she has read the names of
OL,20,Fmurdered women and girls in Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/15
