OL,3,C'Coronation Street storyline made me
OL,4,Cseek help from abusive partner'
OL,6,FShe told ITV Tyne Tees: "The future is
OL,7,Fhere. The women and girls in our
OL,8,Fcountry have made it completely clear
OL,9,Fthat they don't feel safe.
OL,11,F"The rates of domestic abuse, sexual
OL,12,Fviolence, exploitation, stalking I
OL,13,Fwouldn't expect to see an enormous
OL,14,Fspike if we if we didn't do anything
OL,15,Fbecause we're at the point of enormous
OL,16,Fspike."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/15
