OL,3,C'Coronation Street storyline made me
OL,4,Cseek help from abusive partner'
OL,6,FThe Minister for Safeguarding and
OL,7,FViolence Against Women and Girls is
OL,8,Falso looking at the issue from the
OL,9,Fother end of the justice process -
OL,10,Fsentencing.
OL,12,F"I think that if you were to look at
OL,13,Fthe kind of sentences that are given
OL,14,Fout in some of the worst cases of
OL,15,Fabuses against women, girls, there is
OL,16,Fundoubtedly a piece of work that has
OL,17,Fto be done around sentencing," she
OL,18,Fcontinued.
