OL,6,F"And the Lord Chancellor has announced
OL,7,Fthat she will do a sentencing review
OL,8,Fand absolutely what will be being fed
OL,9,Finto that sentencing review is some of
OL,10,Fthe the clear discrepancies when the
OL,11,Fvictims of those crimes are women."
OL,13,FSomeone who knows all too well the
OL,14,Fpain of losing a loved one at the
OL,15,Fhands of a man - and has battled the
OL,16,Fjustice system herself - is Doreen
OL,17,FSoulsby.
