OL,3,C'Coronation Street storyline made me
OL,4,Cseek help from abusive partner'
OL,6,FHer daughter Joanne Tulip was 29 when
OL,7,Fher body was found in Northumberland
OL,8,Fon Christmas day in 1997. She had been
OL,9,Fstabbed 60 times by Steven Ling.
OL,11,FThe loss of her daughter in such a
OL,12,Fbrutal way has brought Doreen a
OL,13,Flifetime of anguish.
OL,15,F"At lunchtime when everybody's eating
OL,16,Ftheir Christmas lunch, we were
OL,17,Fidentifying Joanne," she said. "Even
OL,18,Fafter all this time, I cannot have a
OL,19,FChristmas Day with my family.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/15
