OL,3,C'Coronation Street storyline made me
OL,4,Cseek help from abusive partner'
OL,6,FDoreen bitterly appealed that
OL,7,Fdecision, arguing that while Ling
OL,8,Faccepts he raped her daughter, that
OL,9,Frape charge was ordered to lay on
OL,10,Ffile, meaning he did not have to sign
OL,11,Fthe Sex Offenders' Register.
OL,13,FThe bereaved mother believes this
OL,14,Fplaces other women in danger.
OL,16,FJoanne joins the ongoing roll call of
OL,17,Fwomen and girls who have been killed
OL,18,Fby men or boys in the North East
OL,19,Fincluding in recent years Holly
OL,20,FNewton, Melissa Eastick and Alice
OL,21,FRuggles.
