OL,3,C'Coronation Street storyline made me
OL,4,Cseek help from abusive partner'
OL,6,FFigures show around one woman is
OL,7,Fkilled every three days by men.
OL,9,FIt is widely agreed that a lot of
OL,10,Fviolence against women and girls
OL,11,Fdevelops in or from a personal
OL,12,Frelationship, so the Domestic Abuse
OL,13,FAct 2021 is deliberately broad,
OL,14,Fincluding crimes such as sexual
OL,15,Fassault and coercive control.
OL,17,FThe government has pledged to halve
OL,18,Fviolence against women and girls
OL,19,Fwithin the next 10 years.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/15
