OL,6,FAs Becky encourages victims to seek
OL,7,Fsupport, those who supported her have
OL,8,Fwelcomed the government's commitment.
OL,10,FLaura Seabohm, from WWIN, said: "Every
OL,11,Fgovernment department, every minister,
OL,12,Fwill need to think about domestic
OL,13,Fabuse within their particular work-
OL,14,Fstream. And we think that's got to be
OL,15,Fa good thing.
