OL,6,F"There might also be greater
OL,7,Fopportunities to fund things like
OL,8,Fpreventative work, really go upstream
OL,9,Fand work with children and young
OL,10,Fpeople around domestic abuse to really
OL,11,Fprevent any perpetrators for the
OL,12,Ffuture."
OL,14,FIf you or someone you know is
OL,15,Fsuffering from domestic abuse - you
OL,16,Fcan find support and advice here.
